cs.DL, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.HC 

The paper describes a semantic wiki interface for OpenMath content dictionaries, which involves aspects of digital libraries (cs.DL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for semantic processing, software engineering (cs.SE) for developing the SWiM system, cybernetics (cs.CY) for the use of semantic technologies, and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) for the user interface design.
